Rounded out 2022 with a handful of art-collabs with friends, artists, and projects I really admire & respect. Got caught up with the holiday rush with family/kiddos for a bit, but am getting back into the swing of things on the art & animation front now and will share a bunch of what I've been up to soon - including this super fun piece I was invited by the homies @fvckrender & @gab.jet.ski to contribute to their project @90s_kids_club a couple months ago.
